data.description: **Eligible VA Assumable Loan at 2.5%**  Welcome to the epitome of upscale living in the heart of the Veramindi neighborhood, the gateway to the enchanting Texas Hill Country. This exquisite 4-bedroom, 3.5-bathroom residence showcases a gourmet kitchen with a generous island that serves as a haven for culinary enthusiasts and entertainers alike. The open concept living area is bathed in natural light streaming through huge picture windows, creating an inviting space that seamlessly blends contemporary design with the warmth of Texas charm.    Step into relaxation on the screened-in porch, a perfect retreat for enjoying the outdoors in comfort. The convenience of automatic shades adds a touch of modern luxury, allowing you to effortlessly control the ambiance. The masterful design extends to a guest suite with an ensuite bathroom, providing a private oasis for visitors or an additional comfort zone for the family. Nestled in the Veramindi neighborhood, just minutes away from the historical charm of Gruene, TX, and the vibrant downtown New Braunfels, this residence offers the perfect balance of tranquility and accessibility.    Beyond the charm of the home itself, Veramindi stands out as a golf cart community, allowing residents to explore the neighborhood with ease. Within the community, amenities abound with a refreshing pool to beat the Texas heat and a cozy coffee shop providing a delightful social space. Make every day a retreat in this stunning residence, where the Veramindi lifestyle seamlessly blends modern luxury with the timeless allure of the Texas Hill Country. Schedule a showing and experience the captivating fusion of elegance and convenience that awaits you.
